        -[0m[2m The `[0m[2mdecrement[0m[2m()` method[0m[2m does[0m[2m have[0m[2m a guard[0m[2m `[0m[2mif self[0m[2m._stock[0m[2m >= quantity[0m[2m`, but[0m[2m there's no[0m[2m synchronization[0m[2m between `[0m[2mcheck_stock[0m[2m()` and[0m[2m `de[0m[2mcrement()[0m[2m`
     
