        - This[0m[2m results[0m[2m in a[0m[2m customer being[0m[2m charged but[0m[2m receiving nothing[0m[2m
     
     3[0m[2m. **[0m[2mDuplicate Charges[0m[2m ([0m[2mpotential[0m[2m,[0m[2m mentioned[0m[2m in the[0m[2m requirements)**[0m[2m:[0m[2m
        - Looking[0m[2m at `[0m[2mpayments[0m[2m.py`,[0m[2m the `[0m[2mcharge()`[0m[2m method doesn't[0m[2m check if[0m[2m an `[0m[2morder_id[0m[2m` was[0m[2m already charged[0m[2m
        - If[0m[2m called[0m[2m twice with[0m[2m the same[0m[2m `[0m[2morder_id[0m[2m`, it[0m[2m would create[0m[2m duplicate[0m[2m charges[0m[2m
     
     **[0m[2mThe fix[0m[2m:**[0m[2m
     
     To[0m[2m fix this[0m[2m, I[0m[2m need to[0m[2m ensure[0m[2m:[0m[2m
     1.[0m[2m **Atomic[0m[2m stock[0m[2m check-and[0m[2m-de[0m[2mcrement**:[0m[2m The inventory[0m[2m check and[0m[2m decrement must[0m[2m be[0m[2m done[0m[2m atom[0m[2mically under[0m[2m a[0m[2m lock[0m[2m
