     3.[0m[2m **Id[0m[2mempotent[0m[2m charging[0m[2m**: Ensure[0m[2m we[0m[2m don't charge[0m[2m the same[0m[2m order twice[0m[2m
     
     The[0m[2m general[0m[2m pattern for[0m[2m reliable[0m[2m checkout is[0m[2m:
